bacci.giovanni.deunifier.DeUniFier.seq

Class HashPointersMultiSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • bacci.giovanni.deunifier.DeUniFier.seq.HashPointersMultiSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequence, Serializable, Comparable<Sequence>

    public class HashPointersMultiSequence
extends Object
implements Sequence
    Sequence class that convert each sequence into an hash code using String.hashCode() methods. This class has to be used in couple with FastaPointersSequences class and each sequences index has to be stored using the addIndex(FastaPointersSequences, int) method
    Author:
    Giovanni Bacci
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
